#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:6
msgid "$endswith"
msgstr "$endswith"

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:8
msgid "Usage: **$endswith(text,suffix)**"
msgstr "Gebruik: **$endswith(tekst,suffix)**"

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:9
msgid "Category: conditional"
msgstr "Categorie: voorwaardelijk"

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:10
msgid "Implemented: Picard 1.4"
msgstr "Geïmplementeerd: Picard 1.4"

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:12
msgid "**Description:**"
msgstr "**Beschrijving:**"

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:14
msgid ""
"Returns true if ``text`` ends with ``suffix``.  Note that the comparison is "
"case-sensitive."
msgstr ""
"Retourneert ``waar`` als ``tekst`` eindigt op ``suffix``. Let op: de "
"vergelijking is hoofdlettergevoelig."

#: ../../functions/func_endswith.rst:20
msgid ""
"Formatting the code using characters such as spaces, tabs or newlines can "
"affect the result of the function."
msgstr ""
"Het schrijven van de code met tekens zoals spaties, inspringingen of "
"regelafbrekingen kan het resultaat van de functie beïnvloeden."

